sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant B as Browser
  participant A as Express API
  participant N as Neo4j
  U->>B: Submit email/password
  B->>A: POST /api/auth/login
  A->>N: Match user by normalized email
  N-->>A: User + password hash
  A->>A: bcrypt compare + sign JWT
  A->>N: Store hashed refresh session
  A-->>B: Set HttpOnly cookies + user JSON
  B->>A: GET /api/dashboard
  A-->>B: Social graph dashboard
